<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA516_06_IH_0002</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema516_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_06_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2">
          <span lang="y">넓이 단위 사이의 관계를 알아보려고 합니다.</span>
          <span class="nemo"></span>안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="col flex dir_col align_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA516_06_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">1 m</p>
              <p class="text2">1 m</p>
              <p class="text3">1 ㎡</p>
              <div class="input_position">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="100" class="w_136"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>㎝</span>
              </div>
              <div class="input_position">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>㎝</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <span>1 ㎡=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="10000" class="w_136"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>㎠</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col flex dir_col align_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA516_06_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">1 ㎞</p>
              <p class="text2">1 ㎞</p>
              <p class="text3">1 ㎢</p>
              <div class="input_position">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1000"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>m</span>
              </div>
              <div class="input_position">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1000"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>m</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <span>1 ㎢=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="1000000" class="w_136"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>㎡</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="text_bullet">
                  <span lang="y">1 m=100 ㎝</span>
                  ➔
                  <span lang="y">1 ㎡=10000 ㎠</span>
                </p>
                <p class="text_bullet">
                  <span lang="y">1 ㎞=1000 m</span>
                  ➔
                  <span lang="y">1 ㎢=1000000 ㎡</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
